      <title>法国得到预算警告，因为DBRS评级为负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/france-gets-budget-warning-as-dbrs-turns-negative-on-rating</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Morningstar DBRS对法国信誉的评估产生了负面的看法，这增加了对国防支出的需求日益增长的要求和持续存在政治不稳定风险的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/france-gets-budget-warning-as-dbrs-turns-negative-on-rating</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 13:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
