    <item>
      <title>旅行禁令举起争议后，安德鲁·泰特（Andrew Tate）回到罗马尼亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/andrew-tate-back-in-romania-after-travel-ban-lifting-controversy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自称为“厌恶女性”的影响者安德鲁·泰特（Andrew Tate）和他的兄弟特里斯坦（Tristan）在正在进行的犯罪调查中返回罗马尼亚进行警察检查，否认特朗普政府迫使当局迫使当局结束旅行禁令，并允许他们在美国度过最后几周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/andrew-tate-back-in-romania-after-travel-ban-lifting-controversy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 07:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本，中国讨论经济，因为美国关税压力上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/japan-china-south-korea-meet-as-us-tariff-pressure-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本和中国于周六在东京进行了六年的第一次经济对话，这项活动旨在减轻亚洲巨人面对美国贸易压力时的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/japan-china-south-korea-meet-as-us-tariff-pressure-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 04:07:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国希望快速欧盟国防交易淡入武器基金访问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/uk-hopes-of-quick-eu-defense-deal-fade-on-weapons-fund-access</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对欧盟新的1,500亿欧元（1620亿美元）的武器基金的机会有限，这引起了人们的担忧，即总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）将无法在5月之前与布鲁塞尔（Brussels）获得一项突破性的防御协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/uk-hopes-of-quick-eu-defense-deal-fade-on-weapons-fund-access</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 19:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管停火，但卢旺达支持的叛军扩大了刚果的土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rwanda-backed-rebels-expand-control-of-congo-despite-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达支持的M23叛军在刚果民主共和国占领了第三个主要城镇，将其束缚扩大到该国矿产丰富的东部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rwanda-backed-rebels-expand-control-of-congo-despite-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
